description:
Student number 1. A transfer student from Private 17 Gakuen based on Kaiba`s orders. She has extraordinary assassination powers and is an elite assassin belonging to the family known as Azuma of the East. She is resolved to protect http://anidb.net/ch62176 [Haru] after having been exposed to her warmth.
Source: ANN
name: Azuma Tokaku
